{"tid":1656334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇梅島初體驗！袁嘉敏素顏水着派福利","createTime":"2019-10-15T14:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T04:10:47.000Z","uid":147522,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77b761ad446203c7d8a155df3abf7ba383bbf651","tid":1656334,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REjruCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREjruCv.jpg&h=ca121f02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVtf7pd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVtf7pd.jpg&h=3ab11c62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/220350_a375b459d0ec1a8707963370485dfd58.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F220350_a375b459d0ec1a8707963370485dfd58.jpeg&h=c0188191&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/220353_6fde00b47d613097a856f4c50f18abe8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F220353_6fde00b47d613097a856f4c50f18abe8.jpeg&h=4eb8eb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有34D豐滿上圍嘅前港姐袁嘉敏（Candy），雖然感情生活Dry到爆，但單身一樣可以活得精彩，近日佢就一個人去咗泰國嘅蘇梅島旅行，仲拍片大方派福利！片入面着一件頭泳衣嘅Candy大騷驕人身材，並留言：「第一次來到蘇梅島，睡到九點多，鳥兒的歌聲叫醒了我，馬上穿上泳衣，因為十點要坐船出海去小島游泳，沒有化妝沒有梳頭髮，剛起來的樣子希望大家不介意。」網友紛紛大讚佢素顏一樣省鏡，仲有網民搞笑留言：「咁火辣 泳池水都變滾水🔥🔥🔥」認真口甜舌滑！"},{"pid":"e81bb7a4b83a5a7823a8c9180800c14e8a4a070f","tid":1656334,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢個大媽煩夠未？"},{"pid":"ef71b099f6b186a5196005bc5ece9021e146e451","tid":1656334,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"仲要係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d208a6df1f6acba8b3e9b9d93ec97a42a494d5","tid":1656334,"uid":73848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":